records.name: Swarn By Hawks - Free Room Upgrade,30 Mints Spa, Guided Snorkeling Tour

location.address: The Hawks Kamadhoo Shore Tank Copy Goalhi

descriptions.direction: Located in Kamadhoo, Swarn by Hawks Hotels is near the beach. Travelers eager for a bit of culture can stop by The Dutch Onion Museum, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Kihaadhuffaru Island Beach and Hanifaru Bay. Nelivaru Finolhu and Hurawalhi Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. With scuba diving, snorkeling, and fishing nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: Experience an abundance of unparalleled facilities and features at Wings by Hawks Hotels.Maintain seamless communication using the complimentary Wi-Fi at guest house. During leisurely days and evenings, on-site amenities such as daily housekeeping enable you to fully enjoy your accommodation. At Wings by Hawks Hotels, every guestroom is provided with convenient amenities and fittings to ensure a comfortable stay. Elevate your experience at guest house with the knowledge that certain rooms are equipped with air conditioning, ensuring a more pleasant stay for you.
